msgstr ""

#: ../../../../getting-started/mix-otp/docs-tests-and-with.markdown:348
msgid "So far we have only written unit tests, typically testing a single module directly. However, in order to make `KVServer.Command.run/1` testable as a unit we would need to change its implementation to not send commands directly to the `KV.Registry` process but instead pass a server as argument. For example, we would need to change `run`'s signature to `def run(command, pid)` and then change all clauses accordingly:"
