#: ../../../../getting-started/mix-otp/docs-tests-and-with.markdown:350
msgid "```elixir\n"
"def run({:create, bucket}, pid) do\n"
"  KV.Registry.create(pid, bucket)\n"
"  {:ok, \"OK\\r\\n\"}\n"
"end"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../getting-started/mix-otp/docs-tests-and-with.markdown:356
msgid "# ... other run clauses ...\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

